Why this is happening
The Arch ecosystem relies on a "Tier 1" and "Tier 2" mirror system.

Tier 1: Syncs directly from the Arch masters.

Tier 2: Syncs from Tier 1.

If your script hits a Tier 2 mirror that hasn't synced yet, or a mirror that's physically too far away (causing those 5-second timeouts), pacman will just hang.

